'''烏維·鮑爾'''（{{lang-de|Uwe Boll}}，{{IPA-de|ˈuːvə ˈbɔl}}，{{bd|1965年|6月22日}}）<ref name="Curr Bio">{{cite book|title=Current Biography Yearbook 2010|url=https://archive.org/details/currentbiography2010unse|year=2010|publisher=H.W. Wilson|location=Ipswich, MA|isbn=9780824211134|pages=[https://archive.org/details/currentbiography2010unse/page/53 53]–56|chapter=Boll, Uwe}}</ref>是一位德國男導演、製片人、編劇和演員，外號「魔人烏波」<ref>{{cite news|title=不如歸去！世上最爛導演魔人烏波宣告退休|url=https://tw.movies.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%B8%E5%8E%BB-%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E7%88%9B%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E9%AD%94%E4%BA%BA%E7%83%8F%E6%B3%A2%E5%AE%A3%E5%91%8A%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91-182202935.html|publisher=[[Yahoo奇摩|Yahoo奇摩]]|date=2016-10-29|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101104331/https://tw.movies.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%B8%E5%8E%BB-%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E7%88%9B%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E9%AD%94%E4%BA%BA%E7%83%8F%E6%B3%A2%E5%AE%A3%E5%91%8A%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91-182202935.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鮑爾執導的電影其中有多部改編自[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]。他的電影的資助大多來自Capture Events And Film Production和他自己的製片公司[[Boll_KG|Boll KG]]。

鮑爾的許多電影成本都不高，且大都獲得了負面評價，其中2005年的《[[異形鬼屋|異形鬼屋]]》被認為是史上最糟糕的電影之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sZOby9yQAOM |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-07-04 |archive-date=2015-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151214155808/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sZOby9yQAOM |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但也因此使他聞名。

2016年10月，鮑爾宣布他打算從電影界退休，主要因為[[DVD|DVD]]和[[藍光光碟|藍光]]銷售上的衰落，並指出，從2005年開始，他不得不出自己的錢來拍電影<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jagernauth|first1=Kevin|title=Uwe Boll Announces His Retirement From Filmmaking|url=http://theplaylist.net/uwe-boll-announces-retirement-filmmaking-20161026/?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter|website=The Playlist|accessdate=2016-10-26|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224122422/https://theplaylist.net/uwe-boll-announces-retirement-filmmaking-20161026/?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Metro">{{cite web|last1=Crouse|first1=Richard|title='The market is dead': Schlock director Uwe Boll’s Rampage of terrible films is finished|url=http://www.metronews.ca/entertainment/2016/10/20/director-uwe-boll-rampage-of-terrible-films-is-finished.html|website=Metronews.ca|accessdate=2016-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027054613/http://www.metronews.ca/entertainment/2016/10/20/director-uwe-boll-rampage-of-terrible-films-is-finished.html|archive-date=2016-10-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==早期生活==
烏維·鮑爾出生於[[韦默尔斯基兴|韦默尔斯基兴]]。他曾就讀於[[科隆大學|科隆大學]]和[[錫根大學|錫根大學]]，並獲得了博士學位<ref>Catalogue of the German National Library: Uwe Boll, [http://d-nb.info/94129529X ''Die Gattung Serie und ihre Genres''] {{Wayback|url=http://d-nb.info/94129529X |date=20201117152129 }}, Inaugural-Dissertation, Universität Siegen, 1994</ref>。

10歲時，在看了[[馬龍·白蘭度|馬龍·白蘭度]]的1962年電影《[[叛艦喋血記_(1962年電影)|叛艦喋血記]]》後決定進入電影業<ref name="lrr">{{cite web|url=http://loadingreadyrun.com/videos/view/330/An-Interview-with-Uwe-Boll|title=An Interview with Uwe Boll|date=2008-05-26|work=[[LoadingReadyRun|LoadingReadyRun]]|accessdate=2009-09-15|archive-date=2009-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090928045016/http://loadingreadyrun.com/videos/view/330/An-Interview-with-Uwe-Boll|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==餐飲業==
從電影產業退休後，波爾進入了餐飲業。他想成為餐廳老闆的願望來自他自己對美食的熱愛。2015年，他在認為缺乏德國美食的[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]開了間包豪斯餐廳（Bauhaus Restaurant）<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|url=http://vacay.ca/2015/05/bauhaus-brings-culinary-art-to-vancouver/|title=Bauhaus brings culinary art to Vancouver|last=Brijbassi|first=Adrian|date=2015-05-18|website=Vacay.ca|access-date=2018-07-02|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702093620/http://vacay.ca/2015/05/bauhaus-brings-culinary-art-to-vancouver/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/bauhaus-uwe-boll-50-best-1.4068136|title=Is the 'world's worst director' becoming one of Canada's best restaurateurs?|last=Yeung|first=Lien|date=2017-04-17|work=[[CBC_News|CBC News]]|access-date=2018-07-02|archive-date=2018-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706190651/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/bauhaus-uwe-boll-50-best-1.4068136|dead-url=no}}</ref>。包豪斯獲得了當地和國際美食評論家的總體正面評價。該餐廳在2016年加拿大100家最佳餐廳名單中排名第37位<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://canadas100best.com/canadas-100-best-restaurants-2016/#1466432791843-4e4ebef9-4d33|title=Canada's 100 Best Restaurants 2016|work=Canada’s 100 Best|access-date=2018-07-02|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702122006/https://canadas100best.com/canadas-100-best-restaurants-2016/#1466432791843-4e4ebef9-4d33|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它還被列入 2017 年全球50家最佳餐廳探索系列，是僅有的三家加拿大餐廳之一<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theworlds50best.com/discovery/USA-Mid-and-Canada.html|title=USA Mid and Canada|last=The World's 50 Best Restaurants Academy|date=2016|website=The Diners Club® World’s 50 Best Restaurants Academy|access-date=2018-07-02|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702093346/https://www.theworlds50best.com/discovery/USA-Mid-and-Canada.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.straight.com/blogra/898191/vancouver-restaurant-bauhaus-reviled-filmmaker-uwe-boll-makes-international-dining|title=Vancouver restaurant Bauhaus, by reviled filmmaker Uwe Boll, makes international dining list|last=Takeuchi|first=Craig|date=2017-04-20|website=[[The_Georgia_Straight|The Georgia Straight]]|access-date=2018-07-02|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702122341/https://www.straight.com/blogra/898191/vancouver-restaurant-bauhaus-reviled-filmmaker-uwe-boll-makes-international-dining|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

波爾談到了他在擁有一家餐廳方面取得的新成功：“這很有趣，對吧？我必須開一家餐廳才能獲得好評。”<ref name=":2" />

2018年初，波爾和妻子{{le|娜塔莉·塔奇|Natalia Tudge|娜塔莉·波爾}}成立了包豪斯集團以擴大業務。該集團收購了溫哥華的Blenheim Pub，將其從一家體育酒吧轉變為一家面向家庭的餐廳<ref name=":5">{{Cite news|url=https://www.straight.com/food/1041071/bauhaus-restaurant-morphs-bauhaus-group-plans-expand-toronto-china|title=Bauhaus Restaurant morphs into Bauhaus Group, with plans to expand to Toronto, China|last=Johnson|first=Gail|date=2018-03-06|work=[[The_Georgia_Straight|The Georgia Straight]]|access-date=2018-07-02|language=en|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702093641/https://www.straight.com/food/1041071/bauhaus-restaurant-morphs-bauhaus-group-plans-expand-toronto-china|dead-url=no}}</ref>。餐廳已關閉<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.yelp.com/biz/the-blenheim-vancouver|title=The Blenheim - CLOSED - Kitsilano - Vancouver, BC, Canada|website=Yelp|language=en|access-date=2019-03-20|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117152045/https://www.yelp.com/biz/the-blenheim-vancouver|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他們還宣布計劃於2019年初在多倫多開設第二家包豪斯餐廳。也計劃在中國開設第三家餐廳，地點選在中国[[海花岛|海花岛]]，將聘用兩名歐洲米其林星級廚師。<ref name=":4">{{Cite news|url=http://scoutmagazine.ca/2018/03/07/gastowns-bauhaus-to-expand-with-restaurants-in-toronto-and-china/|title=Gastown's Bauhaus to Expand with Restaurants in Toronto and China|last=Manager|first=Sponsored Content|date=2018-03-07|work=Scout Magazine|access-date=2018-07-02|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702122007/http://scoutmagazine.ca/2018/03/07/gastowns-bauhaus-to-expand-with-restaurants-in-toronto-and-china/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

